attributionInfo.brokerName: Morel Real Estate Solutions, Inc. dba PAK Home Realty

data.description: Beautiful Modern Remodeled 2 story house with 4 bedroom, 3 baths located in Chula Vista.  Custom tile flooring and tile base board to match throughout the downstairs and upstairs hallway, custom kitchen with custom pullout cabinets and under cabinet LED lighting, newly painted inside with custom colors, newly painted exterior with energy efficient cool coat paint with lifetime warranty, dual energy double pane windows and French doors newly added central Heating and Air, renovated spacious beautiful backyard with beautiful sparkling renovated private pool and heated spa.  Gated RV or trailer parking with lots of room for your toys with ample parking.  Newer appliances included and large wooden 10 x 10 storage shed with a 4 x 8 loft.  33 leased solar panels to save on energy bill with newer upgraded panel box.  Remodeled upstairs bathroom with tiles, newer tub and newer laminate flooring.  2 fireplaces one newly renovated with tile and mahogany mantel and post, second fireplace is in primary bedroom sitting nook.  Newer mahogany waterfall stairs.    Newer recessed lighting throughout the home.  Low maintenance yard with high quality artificial turf and drainage throughout the exterior of home.  Tropical plants surrounding the exterior of home. 2 car garage with loft and epoxy flooring.  Newly installed 55 gallon water heater. Covered dog run on side of home with pavers and drainage.  Close to freeways, shopping, parks, schools & much more!  No HOA ofr MELLOROOS.  This is a must see to enjoy the pristine beauty of this home. Swimming pool and spa next to large tuff shed.  Washer and dryer in garage.  Formal dining room and bedroom downstairs.   Cameras in and around home.
